About this item

  • Waterproof Breathable Material: This dog life vest is made of premium polyester oxford & nylon and mesh fabric, which is not only ripstop but also allow for quick drying and proper drainage. The dog safety lifesaver offers great buoyancy they need while moving freely in the water.
  • Sizes Fits Most Dogs: The life jackets for dogs are available for 6 sizes, from XS to 2XL, meet most sized dogs. Please measure your dog twice to get one size and refer to the dimension chart to choose the right size for your dog. Tips: If your dog is between two sizes, we suggest the larger one.
  • Rescue Handle& Reflective Strips: The dog float vest features a sturdy rescue handle on top, quite convenient to grab it when putting into or aiding leaving water, make your dog controlled totally. And the flotation is also with wide reflective strips, which are especially beneficial for owners who walk their dogs in the evening.
  • Stylish&Eye-Catching Design: The dog flotation vest is out with fashion colors and cute patterns, which attracts person's attention, make your dog to be the focus at pool, beach, or boating with you.
  • Perfect Pratical Design: The dog life preserver is designed with adjustable belt and quick-release buckles to make your dog fit comfortably, easy to put on and take off. Handle on top for quick and easy grabbing. The Heavy-duty D-ring Hook is perfect for dog leash. Reflective stripes and bright colors to enhance maximum visibility.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

About this Item

  • Waterproof Breathable Material: This dog life vest is made of premium polyester oxford & nylon and mesh fabric, which is not only ripstop but also allow for quick drying and proper drainage. The dog safety lifesaver offers great buoyancy they need while moving freely in the water.
  • Sizes Fits Most Dogs: The life jackets for dogs are available for 6 sizes, from XS to 2XL, meet most sized dogs. Please measure your dog twice to get one size and refer to the dimension chart to choose the right size for your dog. Tips: If your dog is between two sizes, we suggest the larger one.
  • Rescue Handle& Reflective Strips: The dog float vest features a sturdy rescue handle on top, quite convenient to grab it when putting into or aiding leaving water, make your dog controlled totally. And the flotation is also with wide reflective strips, which are especially beneficial for owners who walk their dogs in the evening.
  • Stylish&Eye-Catching Design: The dog flotation vest is out with fashion colors and cute patterns, which attracts person's attention, make your dog to be the focus at pool, beach, or boating with you.
  • Perfect Pratical Design: The dog life preserver is designed with adjustable belt and quick-release buckles to make your dog fit comfortably, easy to put on and take off. Handle on top for quick and easy grabbing. The Heavy-duty D-ring Hook is perfect for dog leash. Reflective stripes and bright colors to enhance maximum visibility.
